Elite politicians
Surprisingly, no leader from Murang’a petitioned to include the county in the program but they are enthused about the BBI. We need a push-pull economic agenda that will bring an avocado factory in Kahuro, a medical college at Kirwara hospital and nationalise Gatanga and Michuki polytechnics.
Murang’a people have previously supported political initiatives but never fully benefited from them. Heroes like Kenneth Matiba, Charles Rubia and Mukaru Ng’ang’a paid the ultimate price for speaking out their voice. Honourable Kang’ata should not be cowed.
Elite politicians are at the eating table and are blind to peasants’ cry, unemployment and lack of purchasing power. The king should be jerked into action when the small boy from Murang’a speaks the naked truth.
